_sText:
Battleforce Panic is remake of kobilica's map Kobi Panic. Map hasn't been decompiled, every single block was made by me.

Map description:

     - 64 Spawns
     - 3D Skybox
     - Optimization
     - HDR
     - Radar Overview


and lot more... try out for yourself.


EDIT: New versions of the map has been added. 

Package now contains:

     - Reload version with HDR
     - Reload version without HDR
     - Unlimited Ammo version with HDR
     - Unlimited Ammo version without HDR
